sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Module Edit Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open create/update module page
    UI->>LW: mount(module)
    LW->>DB: Load module (if existing) + institutes
    DB-->>LW: Existing values and options
    LW-->>UI: Render module form

    User->>UI: Choose institute
    UI->>LW: updatedInstituteId(value)
    LW->>DB: Query programme options by institute
    DB-->>LW: Filtered programmes
    LW-->>UI: Re-render dependent select

    User->>UI: Save module
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert/update module + relations
    DB-->>LW: Persisted module
    LW-->>UI: Success toast (new: redirect to edit page)
